Mark and Gary welcome back to the show Dan "Jimmy" Lust to discuss the recent story from the tennis world that has Novak Djokovic threatening to file a $4.4 million lawsuit.

Watch Beyond A Reasonable Doubt on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe while you're there.
